- `rnaseq_AXL_log2_tpm`
- `rnaseq_SLFN11_log2_tpm`
- `rnaseq_ASCL2_log2_tpm`

### Dependency outcomes
- `dependency_BRAF`
- `dependency_EGFR`
- `dependency_ERBB2`
- `dependency_KRAS`
- `dependency_RIT1`
- `dependency_KIF18A`
- `dependency_TMED10`
- `dependency_DHX9`
- `dependency_POLR2A`
- `dependency_RPL11`

Each row represents one cancer cell line; no missing values are present.

